Titolo: Garfield Kart

Anno: 2013

Descrizione: Garfield Kart is a kart racing game published by Microids and developed by Artefacts Studio. The game is based on The Garfield Show, which is based on the American comic strip Garfield. Garfield creator Jim Davis was executive producer. The game was released for Microsoft Windows, Macintosh and Nintendo 3DS, iOS, and Android. The iOS and Android versions are no longer available.
A sequel, Garfield Kart: Furious Racing, was released in 2019. This game and its 2019 sequel were the final appearances of the Garfield Show designs of these characters.